incident_updates.body: The fix will be implemented tomorrow 16/12/2022 during the day.

Start time : 15/12/2022 15:09 UTC  Service impact : Customers that would like to add a floating IP to their network will take more time then usual to be implemented Ongoing actions : Our teams have identified the cause of the incident and are currently preparing a fix
